var book = {
	"name": "2 Timothy",
	"numChapters": 4,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29811A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29811A\"></sup>an apostle of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29811B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29811B\"></sup>Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29811C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29811C\"></sup>by the will of God, according to the promise of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29811D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29811D\"></sup>life in Christ Jesus,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29812E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29812E\"></sup>Timothy, my beloved <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29812F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29812F\"></sup>son: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29812G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29812G\"></sup>Grace, mercy <i>and</i> peace from God the Father and Christ Jesus our Lord.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29813H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29813H\"></sup>I thank God, whom I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29813I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29813I\"></sup>serve with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29813J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29813J\"></sup>clear conscience the way my forefathers did, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29813K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29813K\"></sup>as I constantly remember you in my prayers night and day,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29814L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29814L\"></sup>longing to see you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29814M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29814M\"></sup>even as I recall your tears, so that I may be filled with joy.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For I am mindful of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29815N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29815N\"></sup>sincere faith within you, which first dwelt in your grandmother Lois and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29815O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29815O\"></sup>your mother Eunice, and I am sure that <i>it is</i> in you as well.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For this reason I remind you to kindle afresh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29816P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29816P\"></sup>the gift of God which is in you through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29816Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29816Q\"></sup>the laying on of my hands.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For God has not given us a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29817R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29817R\"></sup>spirit of timidity, but of power and love and discipline.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29818S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29818S\"></sup>do not be ashamed of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29818T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29818T\"></sup>testimony of our Lord or of me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29818U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29818U\"></sup>His prisoner, but join with <i>me</i> in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29818V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29818V\"></sup>suffering for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29818W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29818W\"></sup>gospel according to the power of God,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29819X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29819X\"></sup>saved us and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29819Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29819Y\"></sup>called us with a holy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29819Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29819Z\"></sup>calling, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29819AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29819AA\"></sup>not according to our works, but according to His own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29819AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29819AB\"></sup>purpose and grace which was granted us in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29819AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29819AC\"></sup>Christ Jesus from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29819AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29819AD\"></sup>all eternity,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29820AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29820AE\"></sup>now has been revealed by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29820AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29820AF\"></sup>appearing of our Savior <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29820AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29820AG\"></sup>Christ Jesus, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29820AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29820AH\"></sup>abolished death and brought life and immortality to light through the gospel,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29821AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29821AI\"></sup>for which I was appointed a preacher and an apostle and a teacher.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For this reason I also suffer these things, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29822AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29822AJ\"></sup>I am not ashamed; for I know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29822AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29822AK\"></sup>whom I have believed and I am convinced that He is able to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29822AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29822AL\"></sup>guard what I have entrusted to Him until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29822AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29822AM\"></sup>that day.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29823AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29823AN\"></sup>Retain the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29823AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29823AO\"></sup>standard of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29823AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29823AP\"></sup>sound words <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29823AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29823AQ\"></sup>which you have heard from me, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29823AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29823AR\"></sup>faith and love which are in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29823AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29823AS\"></sup>Christ Jesus.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Guard, through the Holy Spirit who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29824AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29824AT\"></sup>dwells in us, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29824AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29824AU\"></sup>treasure which has been entrusted to <i>you</i>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You are aware of the fact that all who are in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29825AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29825AV\"></sup>Asia <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29825AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29825AW\"></sup>turned away from me, among whom are Phygelus and Hermogenes.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The Lord grant mercy to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29826AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29826AX\"></sup>the house of Onesiphorus, for he often refreshed me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29826AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29826AY\"></sup>was not ashamed of my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29826AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29826AZ\"></sup>chains;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>but when he was in Rome, he eagerly searched for me and found me—",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>the Lord grant to him to find mercy from the Lord on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29828BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29828BA\"></sup>that day—and you know very well what services he rendered at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29828BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29828BB\"></sup>Ephesus."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>You therefore, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29829A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29829A\"></sup>son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29829B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29829B\"></sup>be strong in the grace that is in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29829C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29829C\"></sup>Christ Jesus.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29830D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29830D\"></sup>which you have heard from me in the presence of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29830E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29830E\"></sup>many witnesses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29830F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29830F\"></sup>entrust these to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29830G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29830G\"></sup>faithful men who will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29830H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29830H\"></sup>able to teach others also.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29831I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29831I\"></sup>Suffer hardship with <i>me</i>, as a good <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29831J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29831J\"></sup>soldier of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29831K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29831K\"></sup>Christ Jesus.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>No soldier in active service <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29832L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29832L\"></sup>entangles himself in the affairs of everyday life, so that he may please the one who enlisted him as a soldier.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Also if anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29833M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29833M\"></sup>competes as an athlete, he does not win the prize unless he competes according to the rules.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29834N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29834N\"></sup>The hard-working farmer ought to be the first to receive his share of the crops.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Consider what I say, for the Lord will give you understanding in everything.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Remember Jesus Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29836O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29836O\"></sup>risen from the dead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29836P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29836P\"></sup>descendant of David, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29836Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29836Q\"></sup>according to my gospel,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>for which I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29837R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29837R\"></sup>suffer hardship even to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29837S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29837S\"></sup>imprisonment as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29837T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29837T\"></sup>criminal; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29837U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29837U\"></sup>the word of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29837V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29837V\"></sup>is not imprisoned.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For this reason <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29838W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29838W\"></sup>I endure all things for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29838X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29838X\"></sup>the sake of those who are chosen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29838Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29838Y\"></sup>so that they also may obtain the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29838Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29838Z\"></sup>salvation which is in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29838AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29838AA\"></sup>Christ Jesus <i>and</i> with <i>it</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29838AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29838AB\"></sup>eternal glory.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29839AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29839AC\"></sup>It is a trustworthy statement:For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29839AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29839AD\"></sup>if we died with Him, we will also live with Him;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If we endure, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29840AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29840AE\"></sup>we will also reign with Him;If we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29840AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29840AF\"></sup>deny Him, He also will deny us;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If we are faithless, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29841AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29841AG\"></sup>He remains faithful, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29841AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29841AH\"></sup>He cannot deny Himself.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Remind <i>them</i> of these things, and solemnly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29842AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29842AI\"></sup>charge <i>them</i> in the presence of God not to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29842AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29842AJ\"></sup>wrangle about words, which is useless <i>and leads</i> to the ruin of the hearers.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Be diligent to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29843AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29843AK\"></sup>present yourself approved to God as a workman who does not need to be ashamed, accurately handling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29843AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29843AL\"></sup>the word of truth.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29844AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29844AM\"></sup>avoid <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29844AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29844AN\"></sup>worldly <i>and</i> empty chatter, for it will lead to further ungodliness,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and their talk will spread like gangrene. Among them are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29845AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29845AO\"></sup>Hymenaeus and Philetus,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><i>men</i> who have gone astray from the truth saying that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29846AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29846AP\"></sup>the resurrection has already taken place, and they upset <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29846AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29846AQ\"></sup>the faith of some.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Nevertheless, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29847AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29847AR\"></sup>firm foundation of God stands, having this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29847AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29847AS\"></sup>seal, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29847AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29847AT\"></sup>The Lord knows those who are His,” and, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29847AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29847AU\"></sup>Everyone who names the name of the Lord is to abstain from wickedness.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now in a large house there are not only gold and silver vessels, but also vessels of wood and of earthenware, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29848AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29848AV\"></sup>some to honor and some to dishonor.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore, if anyone cleanses himself from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29849AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29849AW\"></sup>these <i>things</i>, he will be a vessel for honor, sanctified, useful to the Master, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29849AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29849AX\"></sup>prepared for every good work.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29850AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29850AY\"></sup>flee from youthful lusts and pursue righteousness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29850AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29850AZ\"></sup>faith, love <i>and</i> peace, with those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29850BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29850BA\"></sup>call on the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29850BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29850BB\"></sup>from a pure heart.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But refuse foolish and ignorant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29851BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29851BC\"></sup>speculations, knowing that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29851BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29851BD\"></sup>produce quarrels.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29852BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29852BE\"></sup>The Lord’s bond-servant must not be quarrelsome, but be kind to all, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29852BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29852BF\"></sup>able to teach, patient when wronged,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29853BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29853BG\"></sup>with gentleness correcting those who are in opposition, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29853BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29853BH\"></sup>if perhaps God may grant them repentance leading to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29853BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29853BI\"></sup>the knowledge of the truth,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and they may come to their senses <i>and escape</i> from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29854BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29854BJ\"></sup>the snare of the devil, having been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29854BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29854BK\"></sup>held captive by him to do his will."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>But realize this, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29855A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29855A\"></sup>in the last days difficult times will come.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For men will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29856B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29856B\"></sup>lovers of self, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29856C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29856C\"></sup>lovers of money, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29856D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29856D\"></sup>boastful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29856E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29856E\"></sup>arrogant, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29856F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29856F\"></sup>revilers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29856G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29856G\"></sup>disobedient to parents, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29856H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29856H\"></sup>ungrateful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29856I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29856I\"></sup>unholy,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29857J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29857J\"></sup>unloving, irreconcilable, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29857K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29857K\"></sup>malicious gossips, without self-control, brutal, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29857L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29857L\"></sup>haters of good,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29858M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29858M\"></sup>treacherous, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29858N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29858N\"></sup>reckless, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29858O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29858O\"></sup>conceited, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29858P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29858P\"></sup>lovers of pleasure rather than lovers of God,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>holding to a form of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29859Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29859Q\"></sup>godliness, although they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29859R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29859R\"></sup>denied its power; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29859S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29859S\"></sup>Avoid such men as these.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For among them are those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29860T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29860T\"></sup>enter into households and captivate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29860U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29860U\"></sup>weak women weighed down with sins, led on by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29860V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29860V\"></sup>various impulses,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>always learning and never able to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29861W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29861W\"></sup>come to the knowledge of the truth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29862X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29862X\"></sup>Jannes and Jambres <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29862Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29862Y\"></sup>opposed Moses, so these <i>men</i> also oppose the truth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29862Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29862Z\"></sup>men of depraved mind, rejected in regard to the faith.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But they will not make further progress; for their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29863AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29863AA\"></sup>folly will be obvious to all, just <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29863AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29863AB\"></sup>as Jannes’s and Jambres’s folly was also.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29864AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29864AC\"></sup>followed my teaching, conduct, purpose, faith, patience, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29864AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29864AD\"></sup>love, perseverance,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29865AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29865AE\"></sup>persecutions, <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29865AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29865AF\"></sup>sufferings, such as happened to me at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29865AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29865AG\"></sup>Antioch, at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29865AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29865AH\"></sup>Iconium <i>and</i> at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29865AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29865AI\"></sup>Lystra; what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29865AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29865AJ\"></sup>persecutions I endured, and out of them all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29865AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29865AK\"></sup>the Lord rescued me!",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Indeed, all who desire to live godly in Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29866AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29866AL\"></sup>will be persecuted.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But evil men and impostors <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29867AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29867AM\"></sup>will proceed <i>from bad</i> to worse, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29867AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29867AN\"></sup>deceiving and being deceived.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You, however, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29868AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29868AO\"></sup>continue in the things you have learned and become convinced of, knowing from whom you have learned <i>them</i>,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29869AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29869AP\"></sup>from childhood you have known <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29869AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29869AQ\"></sup>the sacred writings which are able to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29869AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29869AR\"></sup>give you the wisdom that leads to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29869AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29869AS\"></sup>salvation through faith which is in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29869AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29869AT\"></sup>Christ Jesus.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29870AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29870AU\"></sup>All Scripture is inspired by God and profitable for teaching, for reproof, for correction, for training in righteousness;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29871AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29871AV\"></sup>the man of God may be adequate, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29871AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29871AW\"></sup>equipped for every good work."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29872A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29872A\"></sup>I solemnly charge <i>you</i> in the presence of God and of Christ Jesus, who is to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29872B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29872B\"></sup>judge the living and the dead, and by His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29872C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29872C\"></sup>appearing and His kingdom:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>preach <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29873D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29873D\"></sup>the word; be ready in season <i>and</i> out of season; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29873E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29873E\"></sup>reprove, rebuke, exhort, with great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29873F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29873F\"></sup>patience and instruction.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29874G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29874G\"></sup>the time will come when they will not endure <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29874H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29874H\"></sup>sound doctrine; but <i>wanting</i> to have their ears tickled, they will accumulate for themselves teachers in accordance to their own desires,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29875I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29875I\"></sup>will turn away their ears from the truth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29875J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29875J\"></sup>will turn aside to myths.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29876K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29876K\"></sup>be sober in all things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29876L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29876L\"></sup>endure hardship, do the work of an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29876M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29876M\"></sup>evangelist, fulfill your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29876N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29876N\"></sup>ministry.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For I am already being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29877O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29877O\"></sup>poured out as a drink offering, and the time of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29877P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29877P\"></sup>my departure has come.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29878Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29878Q\"></sup>I have fought the good fight, I have finished <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29878R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29878R\"></sup>the course, I have kept <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29878S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29878S\"></sup>the faith;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>in the future there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29879T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29879T\"></sup>is laid up for me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29879U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29879U\"></sup>the crown of righteousness, which the Lord, the righteous Judge, will award to me on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29879V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29879V\"></sup>that day; and not only to me, but also to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29879W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29879W\"></sup>all who have loved His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29879X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29879X\"></sup>appearing.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29880Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29880Y\"></sup>Make every effort to come to me soon;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29881Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29881Z\"></sup>Demas, having loved <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29881AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29881AA\"></sup>this present world, has deserted me and gone to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29881AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29881AB\"></sup>Thessalonica; Crescens <i>has gone</i> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29881AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29881AC\"></sup>Galatia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29881AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29881AD\"></sup>Titus to Dalmatia.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29882AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29882AE\"></sup>Only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29882AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29882AF\"></sup>Luke is with me. Pick up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29882AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29882AG\"></sup>Mark and bring him with you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29882AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29882AH\"></sup>for he is useful to me for service.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29883AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29883AI\"></sup>Tychicus I have sent to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29883AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29883AJ\"></sup>Ephesus.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When you come bring the cloak which I left at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29884AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29884AK\"></sup>Troas with Carpus, and the books, especially the parchments.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29885AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29885AL\"></sup>Alexander the coppersmith did me much harm; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29885AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29885AM\"></sup>the Lord will repay him according to his deeds.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Be on guard against him yourself, for he vigorously opposed our teaching.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>At my first defense no one supported me, but all deserted me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29887AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29887AN\"></sup>may it not be counted against them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But the Lord stood with me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29888AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29888AO\"></sup>strengthened me, so that through me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29888AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29888AP\"></sup>the proclamation might be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29888AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29888AQ\"></sup>fully accomplished, and that all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29888AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29888AR\"></sup>the Gentiles might hear; and I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29888AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29888AS\"></sup>rescued out of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29888AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29888AT\"></sup>the lion’s mouth.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The Lord will rescue me from every evil deed, and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29889AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29889AU\"></sup>bring me safely to His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29889AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29889AV\"></sup>heavenly kingdom; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29889AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29889AW\"></sup>to Him <i>be</i> the glory forever and ever. Amen.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Greet Prisca and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29890AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29890AX\"></sup>Aquila, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29890AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29890AY\"></sup>the household of Onesiphorus.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29891AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29891AZ\"></sup>Erastus remained at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29891BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29891BA\"></sup>Corinth, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29891BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29891BB\"></sup>Trophimus I left sick at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29891BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29891BC\"></sup>Miletus.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29892BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29892BD\"></sup>Make every effort to come before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29892BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29892BE\"></sup>winter. Eubulus greets you, also Pudens and Linus and Claudia and all the brethren.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29893BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29893BF\"></sup>The Lord be with your spirit. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29893BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29893BG\"></sup>Grace be with you."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;